title: Fables 1-133 (Nahga-Empire)(Vertigo) HIGH QUALITY
description:
With the new video game based on this series coming out, Nahga-Empire saw fit to release new high quality versions of this series. Lots of thanks to them!

What's in this torrent: Every issue of Fables released so far.

What isn't in this torrent: None of the spinoffs, miniseries, or one-shots. Check The Pirate Bay for those. You can start with "Fables: Werewolves of the Heartland", our friend STFmaryville uploaded a nice one.

I would appreciate some patience. This is by far the largest torrent I've ever uploaded, so if I disappear for a bit do not despair, I might disconnect for a bit to play a multiplayer game. I will seed for a long time, and I'd appreciate if a few people to seed as well.
